results.name: Numerator of the product of prime indices of n divided by the sum of prime indices of n, n > 1.
comment: A prime index of n is a number m such that prime(m) divides n. The multiset of prime indices of n is row n of A112798.
xref: Positions of ones are A326155 without the first term.
